# GnuCash Enrichment Implementation Architecture

## Status: Implemented (v1)

All modules have been implemented with full test coverage (293 tests).

## Package Layout

```text
src/gnc_enrich/
  __init__.py
  __main__.py
  cli.py
  config.py
  domain/
    __init__.py
    models.py
  gnucash/
    __init__.py
    loader.py
  email/
    __init__.py
    parser.py
    index.py
  receipt/
    __init__.py
    ocr.py
    repository.py
  matching/
    __init__.py
    email_matcher.py
    receipt_matcher.py
  ml/
    __init__.py
    predictor.py
  review/
    __init__.py
    service.py
    webapp.py
    templates/
      base.html
      review.html
      done.html
      queue.html
  apply/
    __init__.py
    engine.py
  state/
    __init__.py
    repository.py
  services/
    __init__.py
    pipeline.py
```

## Dependencies

- **Python 3.11+**
- `lxml` — GnuCash XML parsing
- `pytesseract` + `Pillow` + `pillow-heif` — Receipt OCR (jpg/jpeg/png/heic/heif)
- `scikit-learn` + `joblib` — ML category prediction
- `flask` + Jinja2 — Review web app + templates
- `requests` — Optional LLM API calls

## Module Status

| Module | Status | Description |
|--------|--------|-------------|
| `config.py` | Done | RunConfig, ApplyConfig, ReviewConfig, LlmConfig dataclasses |
| `domain/models.py` | Done | Transaction, Split, Account, Evidence, Proposal (incl. tx_date/tx_amount/original_description/original_splits), ReviewDecision, AuditEntry, SkipRecord |
| `gnucash/loader.py` | Done | GnuCashLoader (gzip XML), GnuCashWriter (backup + write + new account creation); candidate filter: Unspecified/Imbalance-GBP only, settled transfers excluded, unsettled (one leg target + one own account) marked for transfer queue |
| `email/parser.py` | Done | EmlParser using stdlib email + GBP amount regex; body filtered (HTML stripped, signatures/quoted replies removed) before amount extraction; full body stored |
| `email/index.py` | Done | JSONL-based persistent index with recursive subdir scanning, incremental updates; search requires amount match when amount filter is supplied |
| `receipt/ocr.py` | Done | ReceiptOcrEngine (Tesseract + optional LLM fallback), total/line-item extraction |
| `receipt/repository.py` | Done | ReceiptRepository: list unprocessed, move to processed with conflict naming |
| `matching/email_matcher.py` | Done | Multi-signal scoring (amount required, date proximity, text tokens); emails without matching amounts are excluded |
| `matching/receipt_matcher.py` | Done | One-to-one matching with amount tolerance, double-match prevention |
| `ml/predictor.py` | Done | TF-IDF + SGDClassifier, keyword fallback, refund detection, optional LLM rationale, evidence-driven description enrichment, terse item lookup; populates original tx data in Proposal |
| `review/service.py` | Done | ReviewQueueService: proposal queue, decision capture, skip persistence, evidence-driven enrichment on submit |
| `review/webapp.py` | Done | Flask app with before/after transaction view, queue sorted by date, evidence panel with select/deselect all, evidence approval checkboxes, approve/edit/skip controls |
| `apply/engine.py` | Done | Dry-run report, apply with backup + audit + journal, rollback |
| `state/repository.py` | Done | JSON/JSONL persistence for all state artifacts with schema version headers |
| `services/pipeline.py` | Done | EnrichmentPipeline wiring all components end-to-end |
| `cli.py` | Done | run/review/apply commands with LLM flags, dispatches to real implementations |

